{"tid":2099734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍店定黃店]如果陸陸雞煲同渣哥玩滅聲都叫黃店，咁係咪即係香港人支持無言論自由？","createTime":"2020-07-08T12:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T03:57:17.000Z","uid":9747,"like":37,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2241bbac16cefb37c315dd663bf31f193bdb8c","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"利申左先<br />\n未食過龍門<br />\n唔想食龍門，覺得龍門食人血饅頭既隨便罷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都想鬧我龍衛兵咁你慢慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前2日陸陸雞笑鳩完龍門<br />\n跟著block左幾多人我諗大家都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣哥就抽完水再出個post,新post有冇del comment暫時就未知喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過咁<br />\n呢單野都幾影響香港呢一年堅持要搞既黃色經濟圈既質素<br />\n笑鳩同路人比人扑爆頭先唔講著（雖然佢地d fans話龍門唔係同路人）<br />\n如果滅聲都做得出，而仲可以做黃圈龍頭既話<br />\n咁究竟香港人係點定義黃圈？係咪貼下文宣鬧下政府<br />\n跟著同藍絲做同一樣既野都可以叫黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你會話我鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過講真佢今次既行為直頭係藍，所以連鬥黃既資格都無<br />\n再加上佢地幾間d分化風氣咁撚勁<br />\n難保到時有其他黃店出名又要比佢地屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d出名既黃店都係香港人捧出黎<br />\n如果佢地咁唔接受香港人既批評，去到要block人del comment既程度<br />\n我諗係時候停止吹捧佢地，唔好比機會佢地做黃圈大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫下其他更加humble既黃店仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10999cc3677946437a2bae0e2ac42b1c3af8b60f","tid":2099734,"uid":172248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"60ebe05be9d39e9521fb25d294a290fcbbb99c2e","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10999cc3677946437a2bae0e2ac42b1c3af8b60f","tid":2099734,"uid":172248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"閱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f24db570cb31cd15cbd62e5d820a7e27f060e0","tid":2099734,"uid":20272,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"唔認同佢地&quot;變咗藍店&quot;<br />\n佢地係要玩批鬥圍爐, 你去幫襯第二間黃店就得<br />\n等佢地玩完抽水批鬥搞撚掂先再幫襯過<br />\n我地亦唔洗add on 開post又批鬥佢地<br />\n用返你既力水去攻擊藍店, 紅店"},{"pid":"1e63c5d4c54ac63cae9a76b8b844a1e035c4399d","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e8f24db570cb31cd15cbd62e5d820a7e27f060e0","tid":2099734,"uid":20272,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"唔認同佢地&quot;變咗藍店&quot;<br />\n佢地係要玩批鬥圍爐, 你去幫襯第二間黃店就得<br />\n等佢地玩完抽水批鬥搞撚掂先再幫襯過<br />\n我地亦唔洗add on 開post又批鬥佢地<br />\n用返你既力水去攻擊藍店, 紅店"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"攻擊藍紅店當然要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392d2ca50dbcd24146e75493c943063e8d44fbc6","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"我淨係講左一句陸陸block就比渣哥block埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f579f1c1d854d11c38e268b127930f62b3c5dc3","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8f24db570cb31cd15cbd62e5d820a7e27f060e0","tid":2099734,"uid":20272,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"唔認同佢地&quot;變咗藍店&quot;<br />\n佢地係要玩批鬥圍爐, 你去幫襯第二間黃店就得<br />\n等佢地玩完抽水批鬥搞撚掂先再幫襯過<br />\n我地亦唔洗add on 開post又批鬥佢地<br />\n用返你既力水去攻擊藍店, 紅店"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"渣哥都可以滅人聲<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d60218eed9f390784f584d96d23834e6f75f679","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"本來見無人理諗著由佢沉<br />\n臨訓見到原來渣渣都係滅聲<br />\n推多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷食呢2間黃圈界渣滓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66722e39b356f3e9613c8d8675016c45f08f86fc","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"黃店龍頭笑鳩完同路人仲滅同路人聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4cdf0d442486f0752e4de6ba59905913a9eb9f","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"滅聲經濟圈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b07f0050e1ba0ffd084ad3e2ce654c5d5a644a","tid":2099734,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"預左被龍粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c7bef07c357825b97940be3f514e9df64b3108","tid":2099734,"uid":295761,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"三間都唔食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把默默做野既黃店幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2590064fe2485f5bea84d23bd3cbad3481e5e2d5","tid":2099734,"uid":96091,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"都講明唔係同路人 覺得啲人係搞事咪block囉<br />\n各有各撐啦 屌幾多次佢哋都唔會大和解"},{"pid":"227b86a459e66eac41c70